{{wikipedia}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Uncertain, but supposed to be from the [[Bible]] story of [[Adam]] eating the forbidden fruit, an apple, and it imagined sticking in his throat.

===Noun===
[[Adam]]'s [[apple]]

# The lump in a throat, most visible in [[male]]s, the [[laryngeal prominence]]

